---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="MEDSEN Foundation" lang="en" description="The MEDSEN Foundation funds concrete actions for the health and education of vulnerable children, financed by a share of MEDSEN's company profits.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 via-amber-400 to-senegal-yellow text-gray-900 py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <svg class="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <pattern id="dots" width="4" height="4" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <circle cx="2" cy="2" r="0.5" fill="currentColor"/>
        </pattern>
        <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#dots)"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.293z"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold">MEDSEN Foundation · Corporate social commitment</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-6">
          Profitability<br/>in service of children.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 max-w-2xl">
          We believe an African company can be <strong>profitable and useful</strong>
          at the same time. That's why a percentage of our net profits is automatically
          donated to the MEDSEN Foundation, which funds field actions for the most vulnerable children.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quantified commitment -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <span class="inline-block bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">Our commitment</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          A measurable commitment, not a slogan.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Many companies talk about "social responsibility". We commit with numbers,
          rules and a public annual report.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-amber-100">
          <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-amber-600 mb-2">10 %</div>
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">of net profits</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            donated each fiscal year to the Foundation, written into our bylaws.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-amber-100">
          <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-amber-600 mb-2">100 %</div>
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">direct benefit</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            for children in vulnerable situations (health, schooling, disability, poverty).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-amber-100">
          <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-amber-600 mb-2">1×/yr</div>
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">impact report</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            audited, published on this site, accessible to all.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Action axes -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <span class="inline-block bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">Our focus</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Four concrete action areas.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-amber-500">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">1. Free care for vulnerable families</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Coverage of check-ups, glasses, hearing aids and specialist care
                for children whose families cannot afford the costs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-amber-500">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">2. School health study scholarships</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Funding for nursing, midwifery and medical students who commit to
                practicing for at least 3 years in school health in underserved areas.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-amber-500">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">3. Equipment for underserved schools</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Donations of tablets, first aid kits, basic medical equipment to public
                school infirmaries in rural and peri-urban areas.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-amber-500">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">4. Awareness and health education</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Creation of educational content (videos, comics, workshops) on nutrition,
                hygiene, mental health, reproductive health — distributed free of charge
                in partner schools.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Governance -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">Governance</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Independent governance.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          The MEDSEN Foundation has its own legal entity, separate from the company,
          with its own board of directors.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sante-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-sante-600">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Distinct legal structure</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Senegalese non-profit association with separate accounts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sante-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-sante-600">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Mixed board of directors</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">MEDSEN representatives, independent health professionals, parent associations, qualified personalities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sante-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-sante-600">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Annual external audit</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Accounts certified by an independent auditor, public report.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-sante-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-sante-600">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Public selection criteria</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">All beneficiaries are selected on objective criteria published at the start of each fiscal year.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-amber-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Why this commitment?
      </h2>
      <blockquote class="text-xl text-gray-700 italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
        "We built MEDSEN because we saw, in our own families, children missing out
        on simple care that could have changed their lives. The system didn't see them.
        Our solution makes them visible. But seeing a child isn't enough — you also
        need to be able to help them when their family can't afford it.
        That's exactly the role of the Foundation."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="text-gray-600">— The founding team</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-amber-500">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center text-gray-900">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Want to support the Foundation?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8">
        Institutional partnerships, donations, skills sponsorship, co-financed projects —
        many ways to contribute.
      </p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-lg transition-colors">
        Contact us
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
